<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard - Aplikasi Pertanian</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

    <header class="bg-primary text-white text-center py-3">
        <h1>Selamat Datang di Dashboard Aplikasi Pertanian</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
                <h2>Dashboard Aplikasi Pertanian</h2>
                <p>Anda dapat mengelola data pupuk dan bibit melalui tombol di bawah.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                <a href="/pupuk" class="btn btn-success btn-lg w-100">
                    <h4>Kelola Data Pupuk</h4>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                <a href="/bibit" class="btn btn-warning btn-lg w-100">
                    <h4>Kelola Data Bibit</h4>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

